title: Legends of the Swordsman Scholar
summary: Legends of the Swordsman Scholar ManhwaWoon Hyun passed the Imperial Examination with flying colors and joined the Imperial Palace as a Scholar. However, he soon came to lament his poor and miserable life of dealing with the Crown Prince’s hobbies. Despite such hardships, he didn’t give up and tried his best to learn martial arts. But one day, why a scholar, Woon Hyun, suddenly picked up his brush to conquer the Murim?! Read the adventures of the scholar who passed the Imperial Examination at a young age. Экзамен на учёного, 學士劍傳, 학사검전, Records of the Swordsman Scholar
